comments.body:
was this ever fixed in versions 3.x ?

I am beginning to look into what it would take to change or set the default unit to dip. 
This is actually important enough to be me to announce a bounty if I need to :-) 

edit: when I generate a hello world classic titanium 3.x mobile web app I find this in index.html
require("Ti/App/Properties", function(p) {
	p.setString("ti.ui.defaultunit","system");
});

Does that mean that mobile web is actually now using dip or that system is actually still px?
I'm still looking into this. this might be a closable ticket.
